{"about_the_game":"Eve Of The Storm diverges from traditional survival-building games by incorporating card-based gameplay, challenging players to think about how to maximize benefits from the cards. <br><br>Expand the island by placing terrain block <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/extras/Placing_Block.png?t=1693970412\" /><br><br>Place different buildings to produce and decorate the island<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/extras/PlacingBuilding.png?t=1693970412\" /><br><br>Food is the essential resource to survive in this game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/extras/Food.png?t=1693970412\" /><br><br>Draw cards will cost food and it will increase as time goes on.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/extras/Drawing.png?t=1693970412\" /><br><br>Gear is another important resource, earning enough gear will achieve the final goal of the game.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/extras/Gear.png?t=1693970412\" /><br><br>There are more than 30 cards in the game for players to experience.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/extras/Card_Type.png?t=1693970412\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1693970412","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1693970412","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1693970412","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2587690/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=